d double click on the nodes to see the input and output items.", "height": 100, "width": 420, "color": 1}, "typeVersion": 1, "id": "67462269-311d-4807-b2dd-ca4f2ec0dbef"}, {"name": "12 Hours from now", "type": "n8n-nodes-base.dateTime", "position": [1520, 580], "parameters": {"noticeDateTime": "", "action": "calculate", "value": "={{$now}}", "operation": "add", "duration": 12, "timeUnit": "hours", "dataPropertyName": "data", "options": {}}, "typeVersion": 1, "id": "769258d7-fcd3-4320-a915-c73611cd6533"}, {"name": "Note1", "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote", "position": [1480, 400], "parameters": {"content": "## 1. Simple Way: Using the Date & Time node\nThere are two actions available within the `Date & Time` node:\n1. Calculating a date - adding/substracting minutes,hours, days, etc.\n2. Formatting a date\n\n", "height": 340, "width": 560, "color": 1}, "typeVersion": 1, "id": "b7d85701-f231-41e1-aa4b-bece97a5d724"}, {"name": "Note4", "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote", "position": [1980, 860], "parameters": {"content": "### 2.1 Working with an existing time string\nAs items pass between nodes, n8n saves dates as ISO strings. This means that in order to work with the data as a date again, we need to convert it back using `DateTime.fromISO('yyyy-mm-dd')`\n. Once doing that, we are able to apply date and time function again such as : `{{DateTime.fromISO($json[\"Now\"]).toFormat('yyyy LLL dd')}}`", "height": 320, "width": 480, "color": 1}, "typeVersion": 1, "id": "47f8e8bb-2fbe-4941-a0e2-b93dc740eeb6"}, {"name": "Set times", "type": "n8n-nodes-base.set", "position": [1520, 1020], "parameters": {"keepOnlySet": false, "values": {"string": [{"name": "Now", "value": "={{$now}}"}, {"name": "Current time with seconds", "value": "={{$now.toLocaleString(DateTime.TIME_WITH_SECONDS)}}"}, {"name": "Today", "value": "={{$today}}"}, {"name": "Tomorrow", "value": "={{$today.plus({days: 1})}}"}, {"name": "One hour from now", "value": "={{$now.minus({hours: 1})}}"}, {"name": "Weekday", "value": "={{$today.weekdayLong}}"}]}, "options": {}}, "typeVersion": 1, "id": "f041aa62-b8bd-4b8f-b01c-09a594a6df32"}, {"name": "Edit times", "type": "n8n-nodes-base.set", "position": [2080, 1020], "parameters": {"keepOnlySet": true, "values": {"string": [{"name": "Current time", "value": "={{DateTime.fromISO($json[\"Now\"])}}"}, {"name": "Current time formatted", "value": "={{DateTime.fromISO($json[\"Now\"]).toFormat('yyyy LLL dd')}}"}]}, "options": {}}, "typeVersion": 1, "id": "8da1a79b-5140-4a60-b844-cf79b9386549"}, {"name": "Format - MMMM DD YY", "type": "n8n-nodes-base.dateTime", "position": [1760, 580], "parameters": {"noticeDateTime": "", "action": "format", "value": "={{$now}}", "dataPropertyName": "data", "custom": false, "toFormat": "MMMM DD YYYY", "options": {}}, "typeVersion": 1, "id": "a761dc57-cbd3-4a9a-abd7-0fc5cddbe784"}], "connections": {"Set times": {"main": [[{"node": "Edit times", "type": "main", "index": 0}]]}, "12 Hours from now": {"main": [[{"node": "Format - MMMM DD YY", "type": "main", "index": 0}]]}, "On clicking 'execute'": {"main": [[{"node": "Set times", "type": "main", "index": 0}, {"node": "12 Hours from now", "type": "main", "index": 0}]]}}, "settings": {}, "nodeGroups": []}, "customData": {}, "_source": "/tmp/n8n_corpus/DragonJAR_n8n-workflows-esp/workflows/00203-n8n-fecha-dinamica.json"}